        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter">
                    <ab><title>2 Samuel 17</title>
                        <milestone unit="line" xml:id="Sam2017-P91r-L4" n="4"
                            prev="TKow.02.003.016.xml#Sam2016-P91r-L4" />
                        <l xml:id="Sam2-017-x001"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">יז׳ </foreign>
                        </l>
                        <l n="1" xml:id="Sam2-017-001"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר </foreign>
                            Da ajtty Aḥitofel Avšalomɣa
                            <milestone unit="line" n="5" />
                            sajlajym endi on eki min kisi da turajym da quvajym David artyna bu
                            keceni.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="6" />
                        <l n="2" xml:id="Sam2-017-002"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואבוא </foreign>
                            Da kelimen anyn istine da ol jadaɣan da sarp⟨a⟩laɣan qollu da
                            qaltratymen any
                            <milestone unit="line" n="7" />
                            da qacar bar ol ulus ki birgesine anyn da vatymen osol ol meleḫni jalɣyz
                            ezin.</l>
                        <l n="3" xml:id="Sam2-017-003"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואשיבה</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="8" />
                            Da qajtarymen bar ol ulusnu sana qajtqanlaj ol barysy eltirip ol kisini
                            ki sen izlejsen
                            <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                            bar ol ulus bolur tync.</l>
                        <l n="4" xml:id="Sam2-017-004"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויישר </foreign>
                            Da tiz kerindi ol sez kezlerinde Avšalomnun da kezlerin-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                            de bar qartlarynyn Jisraʾelnin.</l>
                        <l n="5" xml:id="Sam2-017-005"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר </foreign>
                            Da ajtty Avšalom caɣyrɣyn endi daɣyn Ḥušajny
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                            ol Arkini da esitejik ne bardy avzunda daɣyn anyn da.</l>
                        <l n="6" xml:id="Sam2-017-006"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויבוא </foreign>
                            Da keldi Ḥušaj Avšalom-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                            ɣa da ajtty Avšalom anar ajtadoɣac uspu sez kibik sezledi Aḥitofel
                            qylarbizmo osol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                            sezin anyn eger joq sen sezlegin.</l>
                        <l n="7" xml:id="Sam2-017-007"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר </foreign>
                            Da ajtty Ḥušaj Avšalomɣa jaḥsy tivildi ol kenes
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                            ki kenes etti Aḥitofel ol uspu kerette.</l>
                        <l n="8" xml:id="Sam2-017-008"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר </foreign>
                            Da ajtty Ḥušaj sen bilesen osol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                            atanny da osol erenlerin anyn ki baɣatyrlardylar alar da acy
                            ʒanlylardylar alar tuv
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                            ajuv kibik tizde da atan senin ceriv jesisidi da qonmasty ol ulus
                            byla.</l>
                        <l n="9" xml:id="Sam2-017-009"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">הנה </foreign>
                            Muna
                            <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                            ol haligine jasynady birisinde ol cuhurlarnyn jemese birisinde ol orunlarnyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                            da bolɣaj tiškecoq kenetelej alarda baslyqta da esitse ol esitivci da ajtyr
                            <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                            boldu qyranc ulusta ki Avšalom artyna.</l>
                        <l n="10" xml:id="Sam2-017-010"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">והוא </foreign>
                            Da ol daɣyn ceriv jesisidi ki jiregi
                            <milestone unit="line" n="20" />
                            anyn jiregi kibik ol arslannyn jirime jirir šeškenmesti ki biledi bar Jisraʾelni
                            <milestone unit="line" n="21" />
                            baɣatyrdy atyn senin da ceriv elidi kimler ki birgesine anyn.</l>
                        <l n="11" xml:id="Sam2-017-011"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">כי </foreign>
                            Ki men kenes ete-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="22" />
                            men ystyrynma ystyrynsyn sana bar Jisraʾel Dandan da Beʾer Ševaʿɣadejin
                            qus kibik ki
                            <milestone unit="line" n="23" />
                            ol tengiz qatyna keplikke da izlerin senin bolsunlar cerivde.</l>
                        <l n="12" xml:id="Sam2-017-012"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ובאנו </foreign>
                            Da kelibiz anar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="24" />
                            birisine ol orunlarnyn ki tabulsa anda da toḥtarbiz anyn istine ki necik
                            tisedi ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="25" />
                            cyq ol jer istine da qaldyrylmasty anda da bar ol erenlerde ki
                            birgeisine anyn daɣyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="26" />
                            birde.</l>
                        <l n="13" xml:id="Sam2-017-013"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואם </foreign>
                            Da eger saharɣa ystyrynsa da salarlar bar Jisraʾel ol saharɣa snurlar da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="27" />
                            sermerbiz any ol ezengedejin negince ki tabulmasty anda daɣyn
                            kivincikte.</l>
                        <l n="14" xml:id="Sam2-017-014"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="page" n="91v" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                            Da ajtty Avšalom da bar eli Jisraʾelnin jaḥsyraqty kenesi Ḥušajnyn ol
                            Arkinin kenesinden
                            <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                            Aḥitofelnin da H bujurdu buzma osol kenesin Aḥitofelnin ol jaḥsyny
                            keltirmek icin
                            <milestone unit="line" n="3" />
                            H Avšalomɣa osol ol jamanny.</l>
                        <l n="15" xml:id="Sam2-017-015"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויאמר </foreign>
                            Da ajtty Ḥušaj Cadoqqa da Evjatarɣa ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="4" />
                            kohenlerge bulaj da bulaj kenes etti Aḥitofel osol Avšalomnu da osol
                            zaqenlerin Jisraʾel-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="5" />
                            nin da bulaj da bulaj kenes ettim men.</l>
                        <l n="16" xml:id="Sam2-017-016"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ועתה </foreign>
                            Da haligine ijiniz tezce da anlatynyz Davidge
                            <milestone unit="line" n="6" />
                            ajtadoɣac qonmaɣyn bu keceni jylɣalyqlarynda ol midbarnyn da daɣyn asma asqyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="7" />
                            Jardenni maɣat cajpalmaq bolur meleḫke da bar ol ulusqa ki birgesine
                            anyn.</l>
                        <l n="17" xml:id="Sam2-017-017"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויהונתן </foreign>
                            Da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="8" />
                            Jonatan da Aḥimaʿac turarediler ʿEn Roɣelde da bardy ol qaravas da
                            anlatty alarɣa
                            <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                            ki alar barɣajlar da anlatqajlar meleḫke Davidge ki bolalmadylar ezleri
                            kerinme kelme
                            <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                            ol saharɣa.</l>
                        <l n="18" xml:id="Sam2-017-018"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וירא </foreign>
                            Da kerdi alarny neger da anlatty Avšalomɣa da bardylar eksileri-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                            de tezce da keldiler ivin<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied><ref n="1"
                                target="#Sam2-017-fn1" type="noteAnchor" /> kisinin Baḥurimde da
                            anar quju qaḥrasynda da endiler
                            <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                            ary ortasyna anyn.</l>
                        <l n="19" xml:id="Sam2-017-019"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ותקח </foreign>
                            Da aldy ol qatyn da jajdy osol ol qaplavny iz-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                            leri istine ol qujunun da jajdy anyn istine osol ol jancqan budajlarny
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                            da bilinmedi nerse.</l>
                        <l n="20" xml:id="Sam2-017-020"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויבאו </foreign>
                            Da keldiler qullary Avšalomnun ol qatynɣa ol icki-
                            <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                            rige da ajttylar qajdady Aḥimaʿac da Jonatan da ajtty alarɣa ol qatyn astylar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                            osol qladqasyn ol suvlarnyn da izlediler da tapmadylar da qajttylar
                            Jerušalajimge.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                        <l n="21" xml:id="Sam2-017-021"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויהי </foreign>
                            Da edi barɣanlaryndan sortun da cyqtylar ol qujudan da bardylar da
                            anlattylar meleḫke
                            <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                            Davidge da ajttylar Davidge turunuz da asynyz tezce osol ol suvlarny ki
                            bulaj kenes
                            <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                            etti siznin istine Aḥitofel.</l>
                        <l n="22" xml:id="Sam2-017-022"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויקם </foreign>
                            Da turdu David da bar ol ulus ki birgesine anyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="20" />
                            da astylar osol ol Jardenni jarymaɣynadejin ol tannyn birgedejin
                            eksilmedi ki asmaɣaj
                            <milestone unit="line" n="21" />
                            osol Jardenni.</l>
                        <l n="23" xml:id="Sam2-017-023"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואחיתופל </foreign>
                            Da Aḥitofel kerdi ki qylynmady kenesi anyn da jerledi osol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="22" />
                            ol esekni da turdu da bardy ivine saharyna da cavaʾa qyldy eline
                                ivini<supplied reason="lost">n</supplied><ref n="2"
                                target="#Sam2-017-fn2" type="noteAnchor" /> da buvuldu
                            <milestone unit="line" n="23" />
                            da eldi da astraldy zeretinde atasynyn.</l>
                        <l n="24" xml:id="Sam2-017-024"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ודוד </foreign>
                            Da David keldi Maḥanajimge da Avšalom
                            <milestone unit="line" n="24" />
                            asty osol ol Jardenni ol da bar eli Jisraʾelnin birgesine anyn.</l>
                        <l n="25" xml:id="Sam2-017-025"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ואת </foreign>
                            Da osol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="25" />
                            ʿAmasany qojdu Avšalom aɣaraq Joʾav ornuna aɣaraq ol ceriv istine da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="26" />
                            ʿAmasa uvlu kisinin da aty anyn Jitra ol Jisreʾeli ki keldi Aviɣalɣa qyzyna
                            <milestone unit="line" n="27" />
                            Naḥašnyn tuvduɣuna Cerujanyn anasynyn Joʾavnnyn.</l>
                        <l n="26" xml:id="Sam2-017-026"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויחן </foreign>
                            Da toḥtady Jisraʾel
                            <milestone unit="page" n="92r" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                            da Avšalom jerinde ol Gileʿadnyn.</l>
                        <l n="27" xml:id="Sam2-017-027"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויהי </foreign>
                            Da edi kelgecoq David Maḥanajimge da Šovi
                            <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                            uvlu Naḥašnnyn Rabasyndan uvullarynyn ʿAmonnun da Maḫir uvlu ʿAmiʾelnin Lo
                            <milestone unit="line" n="3" />
                            Davardan da Varzilaj ol Gileʿadly Roɣelimden.</l>
                        <l n="28" xml:id="Sam2-017-028"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">משכב </foreign>
                            Tesek da savutlar aɣacly
                            <milestone unit="line" n="4" />
                            da savutlaryn celmekcinin da budajlar da arpalar da un da etken qolos da
                                burc⟨c⟩aq<ref n="3" target="#Sam2-017-fn3" type="noteAnchor" /> da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="5" />
                            bircimekler da itk<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied>n<ref n="4"
                                target="#Sam2-017-fn4" type="noteAnchor" /> jarynalar.</l>
                        <l n="29" xml:id="Sam2-017-029"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ודבש </foreign>
                            Da cyjbal da saryjav da qoj da cyɣytlaryn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="6" />
                            syɣyrnyn juvuttular Davidge da ulusqa ki birgesine anyn asama ki
                            ajttylar ol
                            <milestone unit="line" xml:id="Sam2017-P92r-L7" n="7"
                                next="TKow.02.003.018.xml#Sam2018-P92r-L7" />
                            ulus acty da aryɣandy da suvsaɣandy midbarda.</l>
                    </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
